Package arcade.util

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Graph.Filter
    Defines a filter for edges in a graph
    Solver.Equations
    Defines ODE equations for numerical solvers.
    Solver.Function
    Defines a continuous function.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Box
    Container that maps a key to a tag category and a series of attributes.
    Colors
    Implementation of ColorMap for discrete and continuous color selection.
    Graph
    Container class for directed graph using nodes as hashes.
    Graph.Edge
    Nested class representing a graph edge.
    Graph.Node
    Nested class representing a graph node.
    Loader
    Custom XML file loader that uses SAX parsing to iterate through the XML file.
    Matrix
    Container class for dense and sparse matrix representations.
    Matrix.Value
    Container class for sparse matrix representation.
    MiniBox
    Container that maps a key to a value.
    Parameter
    Container class for parameter with normal distribution and bound checks.
    Parser
    Command line parser built from XML defining the possible commands.
    Parser.Command
    Container class for arguments of a command.
    Solver
    Static utility class implementing various numerical solvers.
